Agnes Aduako (amụrụ na 25 na onwa Disemba , na afọ 1989) bụ onye Ghana na-agba bọọlụ nke na-agba ọsọ dị ka onye na-agbachitere otu egwuregwu bọọlụ ụmụ nwanyị nke mba Ghana
Ọ bụ otu n'ime ndị otu na 2014 African Women's Championship na 2015 African Games na-agba goolu megide Zimbabwe
Na klọb, ọ gbara bọọlụ maka Fabulous Ladies na Ghana.
